You said he was
the best attorney in the city.

120
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:32,927
No, Esther, I told you
he was my best friend.

121
00:04:32,962 --> 00:04:35,296
Which is exactly what you said
about Jeremy Henschell

122
00:04:35,331 --> 00:04:37,081
in tenth grade,
which really meant

123
