153
00:05:48,805 --> 00:05:50,338
What?

154
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,972
I'm just wondering why you're
not getting up to go ask Harvey.

155
00:05:52,008 --> 00:05:53,174
Because I'm not gonna
ask him.

156
00:05:53,176 --> 00:05:55,226
